snippet.textDisplay: Our entire culture including our music is Central Asian including Turkey soo its better to lean towards that only and figure out what Style, beats and Music Suits and Befits our language, as our tastes are relatable soo is language and other things . Go though their music see how relatable to us they sounds even the similarly of language and selection of words in the song or poetry  Or for that matter go through the old kashmiri orignal songs , you can clearly see that pure turkic kashmiri style.... its a clear fact that our culture is different from india and Pakistan respectively soo lets keep it that way ,kindly dont convert our culture into something it has nothing to do with  , that way we'll loose that shine and every last bit of that kashmiriness within our civilization . Punjabi  music style is different and befits properly with Punjabi , same case is with Bollywood and Pakistani music , it befits properly with their attached or relatable cultures or languages , soo is with kawale . Copy pasting  their styles and befitting on kashmiri is not just utterly shameful but heniously unfair also shows ones insecurity , lack of talent,  Poor Quality  , non seriousness, No Self-respect,  zero decorum.  And all these things are enough to degrade and disturb the rich and beautiful culture of ours ... what you have created is pure Cringe!!
